 잊혀지질 않아서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode045-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"프라이빗에 대해서는 말하지 않는 주의지만\n헬로 해피월드! 의 활동을 위해서라면\n어쩔 수 없지……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode045-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"나라는 인간의 일상을 조금만 알려주도록 하마.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode045-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"부활동은 연극부다.\n무언가를 연기할 때 난 진실에 도달하는 느낌을 받거든.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode045-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"응? 진실이란 무엇이냐고?\n셰익스피어도 말했어.\n진실은 모든 것을 평이하게 만든다……","tention":0,"lip